translate chinese izzy10_25a42b94:

    # gl "Hey Twig. Um... [pcname]. It's Izzy."
    gl "嘿，Twig。呃……[pcname]。我是Izzy。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:21
translate chinese izzy10_326e0196:

    # "She sounds down, like she's been crying. I've never heard her like this before. I pull over into a parking lot so that I can talk to her."
    "她听起来很沮丧，好像刚哭过。我以前从未听过她这样。我把车开进停车场，好跟她好好聊聊。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:24
translate chinese izzy10_eb10a115:

    # pc "Hey. Is everything okay?"
    pc "嘿。一切都还好吗？"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:26
translate chinese izzy10_d41d8cd9_1:

    # voice 'voices/izzy_10_2.mp3'
    voice 'voices/izzy_10_2.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:27
translate chinese izzy10_5ecafd77:

    # gl "No, it's not. I fucked up bad."
    gl "不好，糟糕透了。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:29
translate chinese izzy10_d41d8cd9_2:

    # voice 'voices/izzy_10_3.mp3'
    voice 'voices/izzy_10_3.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:30
translate chinese izzy10_420c216a:

    # gl "Devon and I got picked up by the police a couple hours ago. They say they're charging me with possession and intent."
    gl "几个小时前，我和德文被警察抓了。他们说要以持有毒品和意图贩毒的罪名起诉我。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:32
translate chinese izzy10_d41d8cd9_3:

    # voice 'voices/izzy_10_4.mp3'
    voice 'voices/izzy_10_4.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:33
translate chinese izzy10_cdc43134:

    # gl "I don't know what I'm going to do, [pcname]. I'm in a lot of trouble here."
    gl "我不知道该怎么办了，[pcname]。我这下可闯大祸了。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:34
translate chinese izzy10_4814cea8:

    # pc "Oh shit. I'm sorry, Izzy. What can I do?"
    pc "天哪。真抱歉，伊兹。我能帮上什么忙吗？"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:36
translate chinese izzy10_d41d8cd9_4:

    # voice 'voices/izzy_10_5.mp3'
    voice 'voices/izzy_10_5.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:37
translate chinese izzy10_35f5b561:

    # gl "My brothers are probably at home right now, wondering where I am. They need somebody there to watch them. Can you just go sit with them for a bit until my auntie gets there?"
    gl "我弟弟们现在大概在家里，正纳闷我去哪儿了。他们需要有人在那儿照看。你能先去陪陪他们一会儿，直到我姑妈赶到吗？"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:38
translate chinese izzy10_f6efa27a:

    # pc "Yeah, I can do that."
    pc "行，我行。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:40
translate chinese izzy10_d41d8cd9_5:

    # voice 'voices/izzy_10_6.mp3'
    voice 'voices/izzy_10_6.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:41
translate chinese izzy10_68440382:

    # gl "Thanks, Twig."
    gl "谢谢，特威格。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:43
translate chinese izzy10_d41d8cd9_6:

    # voice 'voices/izzy_10_7.mp3'
    voice 'voices/izzy_10_7.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:44
translate chinese izzy10_61b525e8:

    # gl "I don't know what's going to happen to me, but you've been a good friend to me."
    gl "我不知道自己会怎样，但你一直是个好朋友。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:46
translate chinese izzy10_d41d8cd9_7:

    # voice 'voices/izzy_10_8.mp3'
    voice 'voices/izzy_10_8.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:47
translate chinese izzy10_d03ec30f:

    # gl "Thanks for everything."
    gl "谢谢你做的一切。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:48
translate chinese izzy10_6b6f3352:

    # pc "You're welcome, Izzy."
    pc "不客气，伊齐。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:50
translate chinese izzy10_d41d8cd9_8:

    # voice 'voices/izzy_10_9.mp3'
    voice 'voices/izzy_10_9.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:51
translate chinese izzy10_511de65f:

    # gl "I gotta go. Talk to you later, hopefully."
    gl "我得走了。希望之后还能联系上。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:52
translate chinese izzy10_c363031d:

    # pc "Okay. Bye, Izzy."
    pc "好的。再见，伊齐。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:56
translate chinese izzy10_d0995620:

    # "I pull back out onto the streets and start driving over towards Izzy's house."
    "我驶回街道，开始朝伊齐家开去。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:57
translate chinese izzy10_541c797d:

    # "Izzy in jail. Man, that sucks. I wonder if I'll ever even see her again?"
    "伊齐进监狱了。天啊，这太糟了。 不知道我还能不能再见到她？"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:60
translate chinese izzy10_0161d2d8:

    # "At her house, I find the door unlocked. I open it and walk inside."
    "到了她家，发现门没锁。我推门走了进去。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:61
translate chinese izzy10_0d5bc151:

    # pc "Hello? Anybody home?"
    pc "有人吗？家里有人吗？"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:62
translate chinese izzy10_735aa81f:

    # "I can hear the television playing in the living room."
    "我听到客厅里传来了电视机的声音。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:65
translate chinese izzy10_48d7389b:

    # "Then two boys who must be Izzy's little brothers rush out."
    "接着，两个肯定是伊兹弟弟的小男孩冲了出来。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:66
translate chinese izzy10_c3511125:

    # "Older Boy" "Who are you? You better get out of our house!"
    "Older Boy" "你是谁？赶紧滚出我们家！"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:67
translate chinese izzy10_a66a8306:

    # pc "Woah, calm down. I'm one of Izzy's friends. She's going to be uh... late."
    pc "哇，冷静点。我是伊兹的朋友。 她……会晚一点到的。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:68
translate chinese izzy10_807e3ac4:

    # pc "Your auntie is supposed to be coming, but Izzy wanted me to come sit with you until she gets here."
    pc "你们阿姨本来要来的，但伊兹让我先过来陪你们，直到她到。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:71
translate chinese izzy10_1d52908f:

    # "Younger Boy" "Izzy? Who's that?"
    "Younger Boy" "伊兹？那是谁？"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:72
translate chinese izzy10_ecf25c52:

    # "Older Boy" "That's sis, dummy. That's what her friends call her."
    "Older Boy" "那是姐，傻瓜。她朋友都这么叫她。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:73
translate chinese izzy10_9e4c4b50:

    # "Younger Boy" "Oh yeah!"
    "Younger Boy" "哦，对！"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:74
translate chinese izzy10_380c7fa4:

    # "Older Boy" "Okay, you can come sit and watch TV with us, but if you try anything, we'll bust you."
    "Older Boy" "好吧，你可以进来跟我们一起看电视，但要是你敢耍花招，我们就揍你。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:75
translate chinese izzy10_94570d10:

    # pc "All right then."
    pc "行吧。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:78
translate chinese izzy10_be6441de:

    # "I go in and sit on the couch, while they sit on the floor in front of the coffee table, doing homework and watching cartoons on the television."
    "我走进屋里坐在沙发上，而他们坐在咖啡桌前的地板上，一边做作业一边看电视里的动画片。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:79
translate chinese izzy10_98c4afdf:

    # "After sitting for a couple minutes in awkward silence, the older boy turns towards me."
    "在尴尬的沉默中坐了几分钟后，那个大一点的男孩转向我。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:82
translate chinese izzy10_b0063ead:

    # "Older Boy" "What's your name?"
    "Older Boy" "你叫什么名字？"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:83
translate chinese izzy10_784c18d8:

    # pc "[pcname]. What's yours?"
    pc "[pcname]。你呢？"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:84
translate chinese izzy10_ceb1abab:

    # "Older Boy" "I'm Paul. My brother is Stanley."
    "Older Boy" "我叫保罗。我弟弟叫斯坦利。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:85
translate chinese izzy10_70696046:

    # pc "Nice to meet you both."
    pc "很高兴认识你们俩。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:86
translate chinese izzy10_3a7290ac:

    # "Paul" "So, are you one of her boyfriends?"
    "Paul" "所以，你是她男朋友之一吗？"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:87
translate chinese izzy10_2d34af9e:

    # "Paul" "Sis has lots of boyfriends, but she usually doesn't let us meet them."
    "Paul" "“姐有好多男朋友，但她通常不让我们见他们。”"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:88
translate chinese izzy10_fc1855ec:

    # pc "Yeah, I guess I am. We're friends."
    pc "“是啊，我想我算是吧。我们只是朋友。”"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:89
translate chinese izzy10_0b6b2f16:

    # "Stanley" "Where is she? Why isn't she at home?"
    "Stanley" "“她在哪儿？为什么不在家？”"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:92
translate chinese izzy10_e562930a:

    # pc "Well, the police arrested her. She might be going to jail."
    pc "“呃，警察抓了她。她可能要进监狱了。”"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:93
translate chinese izzy10_9d4dc068:

    # "Paul" "Oh. Like mom."
    "Paul" "“哦。就像妈妈那样。”"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:94
translate chinese izzy10_363102ed:

    # "Stanley" "So we'll never see her again?"
    "Stanley" "“那我们再也见不到她了吗？”"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:95
translate chinese izzy10_05948c06:

    # "Paul" "Right."
    "Paul" "“对。”"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:96
translate chinese izzy10_db875c8c:

    # pc "I wouldn't say that. We'll just have to wait to see what happens."
    pc "“我不会这么说的。我们只能等着看会发生什么。”"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:97
translate chinese izzy10_f0cc05be:

    # "Paul" "Yeah, okay."
    "Paul" "嗯，好吧。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:98
translate chinese izzy10_9054da2b:

    # "Stanley" "I don't want sis to go to jail."
    "Stanley" "我不想让姐姐进监狱。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:100
translate chinese izzy10_8c26bb19:

    # pc "She just got busy with something, but she'll be home soon."
    pc "她只是忙点事，很快就会回来的。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:101
translate chinese izzy10_aed5f95e:

    # "Paul" "Really? She's always here when we get off the bus. What'd she get busy with?"
    "Paul" "真的吗？我们下公交车的时候她总是在这儿。她忙什么去了？"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:102
translate chinese izzy10_0d6ab269:

    # pc "Just some stuff she had to do."
    pc "就是有些必须做的事。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:103
translate chinese izzy10_f0cc05be_1:

    # "Paul" "Yeah, okay."
    "Paul" "嗯，好吧。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:104
translate chinese izzy10_5c971f07:

    # "We go back to awkward silence for a few more minutes."
    "我们又陷入了尴尬的沉默，持续了几分钟。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:107
translate chinese izzy10_d9654c38:

    # "Stanley" "Do you know how to do your multiplication tables?"
    "Stanley" "你会背乘法表吗？"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:108
translate chinese izzy10_c0dfc38d:

    # pc "Uh, yeah I do."
    pc "呃，我会。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:109
translate chinese izzy10_5a2c5982:

    # "Stanley" "Could you help me with my homework then? I don't understand this stuff."
    "Stanley" "那你能帮我做做作业吗？我搞不懂这些。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:110
translate chinese izzy10_e85ea253:

    # pc "Sure, let me see what you have there."
    pc "当然，让我看看你有什么。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:113
translate chinese izzy10_b17956ae:

    # "Stanley gets up and sits on the couch next to me, putting his worksheet and book on his lap to show me."
    "斯坦利站起来坐在我旁边的沙发上，把练习册和书放在腿上给我看。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:114
translate chinese izzy10_b975883b:

    # "Stanley" "I know that 8 plus 6 is 14. But this says that 8 times 6 is 48. How the heck does that work?"
    "Stanley" "我知道8加6等于14。但这上面说8乘6等于48。这到底是怎么回事？"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:115
translate chinese izzy10_329fcf1a:

    # pc "So you know how to do addition? 8 plus 8?"
    pc "所以你会加法？8加8？"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:116
translate chinese izzy10_04dda5a7:

    # "Stanley" "Yeah."
    "Stanley" "会。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:117
translate chinese izzy10_1c11dbdd:

    # pc "Well think of multiplication like you're doing addition over and over again."
    pc "那你就把乘法想象成一遍又一遍地做加法。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:118
translate chinese izzy10_b949eaf3:

    # pc "Here, write 8 six times on your paper. Eight six times is eight times six."
    pc "来，在纸上把8写六遍。8乘以6就是8加6。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:119
translate chinese izzy10_b115a24b:

    # "Stanley" "Oh, I get it."
    "Stanley" "哦，我懂了。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:120
translate chinese izzy10_8b68d233:

    # pc "Then put a plus between each of those 8's and add them all together."
    pc "然后在每个8之间加个加号，把它们全加起来。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:121
translate chinese izzy10_e6a0ee82:

    # "He starts adding, writing the number above each of the eights on his page until he reaches the last one that is 48."
    "他开始计算，在纸上每个“8”的上方写上相应的数字，直到最后一个“8”上写下48。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:122
translate chinese izzy10_7d468f4d:

    # "Stanley" "I get it! Wow, you should be a teacher."
    "Stanley" "我懂了！哇，你应该当老师。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:125
translate chinese izzy10_d3d886b1:

    # "I hear the front door open and a woman's voice calls out."
    "我听到前门打开，一个女人的声音喊道。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:126
translate chinese izzy10_e6d98dc8:

    # "Woman" "Boys? Y'all in here?"
    "Woman" "孩子们？你们都在这儿吗？"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:129
translate chinese izzy10_e3c838b3:

    # "The woman, who must be the boy's auntie, walks around the corner and both of them rush up to hug her."
    "那个女人，想必是男孩的阿姨，转过拐角，两个孩子立刻跑过去拥抱她。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:130
translate chinese izzy10_ec0adf9c:

    # "Auntie" "Everything okay here?"
    "Auntie" "“这里一切都好吗？”"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:131
translate chinese izzy10_5e4c7b42:

    # "Paul" "Yeah, we're all good."
    "Paul" "“嗯，我们都没事。”"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:132
translate chinese izzy10_60d1cbf2:

    # "Stanley" "[pcname] was teaching me how to do my times table."
    "Stanley" "“[pcname]正在教我背乘法表。”"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:133
translate chinese izzy10_ad65d7e3:

    # "Auntie" "That's nice of him."
    "Auntie" "“他真好。”"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:134
translate chinese izzy10_31976fc3:

    # "Auntie" "You two go to your room and pack up some clothes. You're going to come stay at my house for a few days, okay?"
    "Auntie" "“你们两个回房间收拾点衣服。接下来几天要来我家住，好吗？”"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:135
translate chinese izzy10_32e2b2bb:

    # "Paul" "Is sis okay?"
    "Paul" "“姐姐没事吧？”"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:136
translate chinese izzy10_d6e45f9a:

    # "Auntie" "She's okay, but she's going to be gone for a bit."
    "Auntie" "“她没事，但要离开一段时间。”"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:137
translate chinese izzy10_e67935e5:

    # "Stanley" "How long?"
    "Stanley" "要多久？"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:138
translate chinese izzy10_1f41c1ac:

    # "Auntie" "I don't know yet honey. Go pack your bags, okay?"
    "Auntie" "我还不清楚，宝贝。去收拾行李吧，好吗？"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:141
translate chinese izzy10_3581e151:

    # "The two boys run off towards their rooms, and I stand up to talk to their auntie."
    "两个男孩跑回房间，我站起来跟他们的阿姨说话。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:142
translate chinese izzy10_f78cee83:

    # "Auntie" "Thanks for coming over and sitting with them for a bit."
    "Auntie" "谢谢你过来陪陪他们一会儿。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:143
translate chinese izzy10_5301b871:

    # pc "Oh, no problem. They seem like good kids."
    pc "哦，没关系。他们看起来是好孩子。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:144
translate chinese izzy10_bd9c1d85:

    # "Auntie" "They are. I wish they didn't have to go through all this. First their mom, now their sister."
    "Auntie" "确实是。真希望他们不必经历这一切。先是妈妈，现在又是姐姐。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:145
translate chinese izzy10_8a42d1af:

    # pc "Is she going to be okay?"
    pc "她会没事吗？"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:146
translate chinese izzy10_74736fd1:

    # "Auntie" "She had a lot of drugs on her when they arrested her and that other boy. She has a couple of priors as well. It doesn't look good."
    "Auntie" "他们逮捕她和那个男孩时，她身上带了很多毒品。她还有几项前科。情况不太妙。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:147
translate chinese izzy10_139f3015:

    # "Auntie" "I've been trying to get her to drop the drugs for a long time."
    "Auntie" "我早就想让她戒毒了。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:148
translate chinese izzy10_5e1c08a1:

    # "Auntie" "But it's hard to take care of two kids with a minimum wage job. Isabel didn't ask for any of this either."
    "Auntie" "但靠最低工资的工作，要照顾两个孩子实在太难了。伊莎贝尔本来也不该遭遇这些的。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:149
translate chinese izzy10_847af3a0:

    # "Auntie" "I don't know how {i}I'm{/i} even going to take care of these boys."
    "Auntie" "我真不知道{i}该{/i}怎么照顾这两个孩子。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:150
translate chinese izzy10_45975e4c:

    # "Auntie" "But, I'll figure it out. Got no other choice."
    "Auntie" "不过，我会想办法的。别无选择。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:151
translate chinese izzy10_527206cb:

    # "Auntie" "Anyways, thanks again. I'll take it from here."
    "Auntie" "总之，再次感谢。接下来就交给我了。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:154
translate chinese izzy10_47574532:

    # "She walks me towards the front door, but before I leave, Paul and Stanley come back out."
    "她送我走到前门，但就在我离开前，保罗和斯坦利又走了出来。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:155
translate chinese izzy10_82761cf4:

    # "Stanley" "Bye, [pcname]! Thanks for helping me with my math."
    "Stanley" "再见啦，[pcname]！谢谢你帮我做数学题。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:156
translate chinese izzy10_0438055e:

    # pc "Bye, you two. Be good. Keep studying."
    pc "再见，你们两个。要乖哦。继续好好学习。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:160
translate chinese izzy10_85086dcf:

    # "I walk out, get into my car, and drive away."
    "我走出门，坐进车里，开车离开了。"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy10.rpy:161
translate chinese izzy10_70ed6fb0:

    # "Damn, I hope Izzy will be okay. Those boys too. This whole situation just sucks."
    "该死，希望伊兹能挺过去。那两个男孩也是。整个局面简直糟透了。"

